<headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 14 at 4:19PM EDT  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...A STRONG THUNDERSTORM WILL AFFECT CENTRAL BEDFORD COUNTY...
At 418 PM EDT, a strong thunderstorm was located over Montvale,
moving east at 20 mph.
Winds in excess of 30 mph and pea size hail are possible with this
storm.
Locations impacted include...
Bedford...
Montvale...
Stewartsville...
Big Island...
Forest...
Coleman Falls...
and Goode.</description>
